summary: This document is a certificate from the Department of Transportation certifying the authenticity of records related to a Gulfstream Aerospace G-IV aircraft. It confirms that the records are maintained by the Aircraft Registration Branch of the Federal Aviation Administration as of August 23, 2021.
keyFacts: The document certifies the authenticity of records pertaining to Gulfstream Aerospace G-IV, serial number JOSS.
The registration number of the aircraft is NI2f0E.
The certification was signed by a Supervisory Legal Instruments Examiner.
It is subject to a protective order.
